OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMoney-off energy scheme set
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fout to avoid blackouts     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Households will be offered discounts on
OL,6, their electricity bills if they cut    
OL,7, peak-time use on a handful of days over
OL,8, the winter, as part of National Grid's 
OL,9, efforts to avoid blackouts.            
OL,11,FThe network operator has announced     
OL,12,Fdetails of the scheme, which it said   
OL,13,Fcould save households up to #100.      
OL,15,FThere will be 12 "test" days initially,
OL,16,Fdesigned to see how customers respond, 
OL,17,Fbetween November and March.            
OL,19,FBut only homes with smart meters will  
OL,20,Fbe able to take part.                  
